title: Gloria Estefan Discography
description:
Unbelievable, but true: nobody put together a discography of Gloria Estefan so far!

So here it is!

It&#039;s a discography of Gloria as a solo artists, the albums she recorded with "Miami Sound Machine" are not included!

The quality is as good as possible (for me), most is in 320.

Enjoy!

And please help seeding!

- Cuts both ways
- Into the light
- Mi tierra
- Christmas through your eyes
- Hold me, thrill me, kiss me
- Abriendo puertas
- Destiny
- Gloria!
- Alma Caribena
- Unwrapped
- 90 millas
- The essential (the only "Best of..." included)
- Diverse (some other tracks not included on her albums)
